description: They look known but I don't think they attend this gym, most likely we've met at a party. This flavor is familiar to me, I'm almost sure we've already tasted each other. I'm gonna break what's left of this wall, I can't stand the urge to touch them and see their faces. I need to tap that ass right now. Breathe, the day is long, this is just the beginning.
